definitions.definition: Any of several small, insectivorous long-nosed mammals , of the family Macroscelididae within the Macroscelidea order, native to Africa .

main_definition: Any of several small, insectivorous long-nosed mammals , of the family Macroscelididae within the Macroscelidea order, native to Africa .

definitions.definition: A former (1967–1993) monetary unit of Zaire , one hundredth of a likuta , and one ten-thousandth of a zaire ; it was issued only in ten sengi coins .

main_definition: ( historical ) A former (1967–1993) monetary unit of Zaire , one hundredth of a likuta , and one ten-thousandth of a zaire ; it was issued only in ten sengi coins .
